Description: Drop untested non-default features
Last-Update: 2024-03-04

This crate is primarily packaged as a dependency to another app, which
doesn't use any feature involving JS or WASM (those being marked
"Untested" in the project's README). In order to simplify packaging and
avoid introducing an unnecessary package in the Debian archive, let's
just patch out those features.
